data.description: Stunning 2020 custom built home on the golf course with just under two acres of property. Three bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, an office downstairs, plus a 455 sq ft bonus room with bathroom upstairs. Vaulted great room with custom fireplace, over 9ft ceilings throughout the home, with custom soft close cabinetry. Waterproof flooring in all bathrooms and laundry. Large covered front and back porches, and underground sprinklers in front and back yard. Drive through gate access to the back yard and walk through gate to flat useable rear acre. Home has a separate 10x10 workshop and an attached three car garage with utility room. Enjoy beautiful sunrises from the back porch, just 10 minutes from Salem, but out of town living! This home is a must see!
